the event that you want to contact LALIGA through the form established for this purpose on the Platform, LALIGA will process your personal data that you submit through this form (email, name, surname, telephone, media to which you belong, section or program, position and country) in order to manage, process and respond to the request you have sent.
The legal basis for the aforementioned purposes is that the processing is necessary for the satisfaction of the legitimate interest of LALIGA under the provisions of art. 6.1 f) of the General Data Protection Regulation consisting of managing your request for information. Before doing so, we inform you that LALIGA has carried out an analysis of proportionality between its legitimate interest and the rights and freedoms of its users, whose conclusions you can request through
