MyAccount is a section within MILIGA where you can consult all the personal information you have provided to LALIGA through any of its assets.
Also, you can complete the user profile you have in the digital ecosystem of LALIGA with the data you consider relevant, modify those data that are incorrect, inaccurate or outdated, as well as delete this data, updating this information in all LALIGA assets where you are registered.
